org.tmatesoft.svn.core.wc2
Class SvnInfo

java.lang.Object
  org.tmatesoft.svn.core.wc2.SvnObject
      org.tmatesoft.svn.core.wc2.SvnInfo

public class SvnInfo
extends SvnObject

Represents information details for versioned item's (located either in a working copy or a repository). When running an SvnInfo operation all collected item information data is packed inside an SvnInfo object.

See Also:
SvnGetInfo
